thread.title: Treasury to Sell $229 Billion in Debt

author: wsjcom
title: Treasury to Sell $229 Billion in Debt
text:
The U.S. Treasury Department will auction $229 billion in securities next week, comprising $181 billion in new debt and $48 billion in previously sold debt. Details (all with minimum denominations of $100):
Monday: $48 billion in 13-week bills, a reopening of an issue first sold on Jan. 25, 2018, maturing July 26, 2018. Cusip number: 912796PR4.
